Can you ever see a world where we return to a slightly slower fashion

00:20:17.136 --> 00:20:21.966
industry, of buying fewer but better quality clothes that last for longer?

00:20:22.706 --> 00:20:26.916
What are some of the other impacts of fashion becoming a disposable item?

